      • diffTables

        public static TableAnswerElement diffTables(TableAnswerElement baseTable,
                                            TableAnswerElement deltaTable,
                                            boolean includeOneTableKeys)
        Computes the difference table of the two tables by taking a "join" on the key columns. If includeOneTableKeys is true, then an "inner join" is done, that is, only keys that are present in both tables are in the output. Otherwise, a "full outer join" is done and any key that is in either table makes it to the output.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the input column metadatas are not equal.
